      "reasoning_chain": "1) Steering needs actuators; actuators bulk up tip. 2) #29: replace mechanical with pneumatic (inflatable steering channels). 3) #1: segment tip into independent inflatable cells. 4) #15 dynamization: cells can be selectively pressurized.",
      "solution": "Soft-robotic endoscope with multiple pneumatic steering chambers: <5 mm OD with full multi-axis steering.",
      "complexity": "medium"
    },

    {
      "id": "MOD-09",
      "source": "Berdyugina & Cavallucci 2023 J. Intell. Manuf. (patent NLP for inventive info)",
      "language": "en",
      "domain": "manufacturing/electronics",
      "problem": "PCB testing throughput vs. defect detection: faster test misses defects.",
      "contradiction_pair": {
        "improving_parameter": "Productivity (#39)",
        "worsening_parameter": "Accuracy of measurement (#28)"
      },
      "inventive_principles": ["#10 Preliminary action", "#24 Mediator", "#28 Mechanics substitution"],
      "reasoning_chain": "1) Faster probing causes contact errors. 2) #28: replace contact probing with optical AOI. 3) #24: machine-vision intermediary verifies defects before electrical retest. 4) #10: train defect classifier in advance.",
      "solution": "Two-stage AOI + targeted electrical retest pipeline: full-board AOI in 5 s; only flagged regions get probed; throughput +40%, escape rate –60%.",
      "complexity": "medium"
