      "reasoning_chain": "1) Liquid absorbs energy but is heavy. 2) #35 + #29: replace liquid with pressurized gas + foam composite. 3) #40 composite skin holds gas; foam absorbs initial impact, gas absorbs peak.",
      "solution": "Composite-skin pneumatic-foam bumper: 30% lighter than liquid bumper, no freeze risk, equal energy absorption.",
