        "solution": "Unbonded flexible riser: a concentric stack of independent functional layers — interlocked steel carcass, polymer pressure barrier, and counter-wound helical steel armour wires — that slide freely during bending while combining to resist all static and fatigue loads. Industry standard for deepwater production in 1500+ m water depth.",
