        "language": "en",
        "domain": "biomedical/electronics",
        "problem": "Acoustic stethoscopes in busy ICUs and emergency departments pick up ambient noise that masks cardiac and lung sounds, leading to diagnostic errors; moving to a quiet room delays care.",
